Is there a JMX Agent running where hcc is hosted?   Is hcc hosted in 
JBOSS?  Then for sure there is a JMX  Agent.   Otherwise, if you running 
hcc in its own JVM, you need to add system properties to enable a JMX 
Agent.  The hcc documentation, 
http://crawler.archive.org/hcc/apidocs/overview-summary.html, points you 
at general JMX documentation for how to do this.  Alternatively, study 
the heritrix wrapper script for example of what to set.

Otherwise, I&#39;m not sure why the lookup is failing.  Can you put hcc 
under a debugger or add in System.out.print statements?

St.Ack

